high_descs: walk through bathroom to face radiator cover next to sink
pick up pink soap bar from radiator cover
wash soap in sink, pick up soap from sink
turn right to face radiator cover
anns.task_desc: put a washed soap bar on radiator cover

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the shelf under the hanging towel.
Pick up the pink soap bar.
Rinse off the soap in the sink.
Turn right and look at the counter again.
Place the soap on the counter, all the way to the right.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a counter.

high_descs: Go to the cabinet to the right of the sink.
Pick up pink bar of soap from the top of the cabinet.
Take the bar of soap to the sink.
Place the bar of soap into the sink and fill the sink with water.
Remove the bar of soap from the sink.
Place the bar of soap back on top of the cupboard next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the bar of soap from the cabinet, into the sink, fill with water, then return to the cabinet.
